<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
      body {
          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
          background-color: #0f172a;
          color: #f1f5f9;
      }

      .title {
        margin: 8px;
      }

      .content {
        margin: 16px 32px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="title">
      <%= image_tag 'email-logo.png' %>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hey, <b><%= @user.display_name %></b>, thanks for signing up for the Gamer-dex!</p>

      <p>
        You're now free to login and:
        <ol>
          <li>Set up your profile (avatar and bio)</li>
          <li>Make friends (we've given you your first friend for free!)</li>
          <li>Create posts with text and/or images (and edit/delete them later)</li>
          <li>View your friends posts in your feed</li>
          <li>Like friends' posts</li>
          <li>Add games to your profile (provided by giantbomb.com)</li>
        </ol>
      </p>
      <p>
        Welcome to our humble community!<br>
        - Kevin <em>(developer)</em>
      </p>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>
